author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Bathroom sink cabinet tips…I’m installing an 18 inch vanity cabinet but want solid blocking for it. I pre-drill the four corners of the 2x8 and use 3 inch GRK Multi-Purpose screws. This provides solid blocking to fasten the cabinet to after drywall installation 🔥#bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
